summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 184 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone property located at 1000 S. Henderson St., from Single family 5000 (SF 5000) to Lowrise Duplex Triplex (LDT) multifamily residential and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Sea Mar Community Health Centers, C.F. 307093, DPD Project 2309015)
